    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">- BF: :[N]EditPrevious with supplied [N] would skip over existing smaller number file and would claim that no substituted file existed. <br>- BF: :[N]EditPrevious with supplied large [N] together with a low original number hogs the CPU because the loop iterates over the entire number range where the resulting offset would be negative.</td>
</tr>
